                </FooterDetails>
                <Header>Green Economy Transition (GET)</Header>
                <Paragraph>By 2020, the GET approach seeks to increase the volume of green financing to 40 per cent of EBRD annual business investment. Safeguarding the environment and strengthening ecosystems help market economies function better and, therefore, are central to the transition process that the EBRD has promoted since its inception.</Paragraph>
            </EntitySourceOfInformation>
            <EntitySourceOfInformation EntitySourceOfInformationId="2118" SortOrder="7">
                <FooterDetails>
